                  r,←⊂'- GetDOTNETVersion - returns 4 elements to describe .NET Version that is in use:'
                  r,←⊂'                     R[1] = 0/1/2: 0=nothing, 1=.net Framework, 2=NET CORE'
                  r,←⊂'                     R[2] = Version (text vector)'
